g.text: We, as Neqat Noor, aspire to become a hub for education, transformation, and

personal development, all driven by dedicated and skilledvolunteers. We firmly believe in the importance of teachinglife skills and citizenship to children and youth.These skills empower them to adapt to a changing world andachieve success in education, employment, and personal goals.Education should be built upon a forward-thinking andcomprehensive vision to empower future generations.
